Loops In Java

1. while loop
    syntax --> 
        while (condition) {
            statement1;
            ...
        }

    // while loop is also known as "Entry Control Loop"


2. for loop
    syntax --> 
        for (initialization; condition; update) {
            statement1;
            ...
        }


3. do while loop
    syntax --> 
        do {
            statement1;
            ...
        } while (condition);

    // Do while loop is also known as "Exit Control Loop"